data.description: Gorgeous Ventura home just built in 2019 on an oversized lot in Kelsey Park! 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, plus a bonus room and a huge backyard - big enough to add a 3rd car garage, shop or pool. Vaulted ceiling throughout the open living room and kitchen. Incredible kitchen with a huge island, extended cabinets, and gas stove. Built-in desk space just off the kitchen leading to the owner's suite.  The owner's suite features a view of the backyard, double vanities, large shower, separate tub and a walk-in closet with built-ins. The bonus room makes for a great playroom or second living area looking out into the backyard.
